OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy morning with a
OL,6,Ffew spots of rain. Sunny intervals and
OL,7,Fshowers developing for the afternoon,
OL,8,Fsome of which may be heavy with the
OL,9,Fodd rumble of thunder. The best of the
OL,10,Fsunniest conditions on western coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers will quickly die out
OL,13,Fthis evening. Then turning cloudier
OL,14,Fwith rain spreading in from the west
OL,15,Fduring the early hours, this
OL,16,Foccasionally heavy for Dumfries and
OL,17,FGalloway.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
