OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA cloudy morning with
OL,6,Foccasional heavy rain at first.
OL,7,FShowers will develop for the
OL,8,Fafternoon, some possibly heavy with
OL,9,Fthe odd rumble of thunder in the west.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,12,FVariable amounts of cloud with showers
OL,13,For a few spells of rain, particularly
OL,14,Facross western areas. Warmer than of
OL,15,Flate, particularly in drier, sunnier
OL,16,Fconditions in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
